=Description=

Standard owned by Adobe:

"The XMP framework is open, extensible, and can accommodate existing metadata schemas. Various standards initiatives are using XMP as their framework of choice for implementation. The extensibility of XMP allows standards to be expressed and carried throughout the workflow. The custom panel capabilities within Adobe applications help ensure that metadata is accessible and viewable within the workflow."
(http://www.adobe.com/products/xmp/standards.html)


